casebody.data:
Jeremiah J. Peters v. Department of Motor Vehicles et al. (10489)

Daly, O’Connell and Norcott, Js.

Argued January 10 decision released January 28, 1992 Douglas T. Barall, for the appellant (defendant). Robert T. Morrin, assistant attorney general, with whom, on the brief, was Richard Blumenthal, attorney general, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
